CommandLineParser The command line parser for SolPicker.

ExecuteSolPicker $Id: package-summary.html,v 1.13 2009/10/16 23:08:53 tizatt Exp $ Consists of a Frame that contains four panels that allow the user to add queries, add configurations, add jobs, and perform jobs.
Log Records all information about the actual program run into a log file
XMLErrorHandler This class handles all errors associated with parsing an xml document.
XMLInputWriter  
XMLParser This class takes the XML file containing all input information and parses it using a Document Object Model (DOM) parser, which creates a hierarchical tree with the tags stored as nodes.
